description: Looking for a tasty way to keep cool on a sunny SoCal day? Then Beach Town Pops is perfect for you! Gourmet ice pops to satisfy your sweet tooth, these terrific treats are not going to let you get away with just having one. Plus, for those who want a mature twist on their pops, a new assortment of alcoholic popsicles are available! Thats right, Booze Pops. Don't miss out, Beach Town Pops is serving up something great today!
name: Beach Town Pops
